      <title>秘鲁不顾国际法庭释放前总统藤森</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/peru-to-free-ex-president-fujimori-defying-international-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[秘鲁将于周四释放被监禁的前总统阿尔贝托·藤森，这是这个安第斯国家对一个将拉丁美洲所有主要经济体视为成员的国际法庭所面临的最严峻的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/peru-to-free-ex-president-fujimori-defying-international-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 22:03:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将拨款 82 亿美元促进 2024 年关键州的铁路建设</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/biden-to-award-8-2-billion-boosting-rail-in-key-2024-states</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情人士透露，总统乔·拜登本周将宣布追加 82 亿美元的铁路资金，以推动潜在项目的发展——包括一条通往拉斯维加斯的高速线路—— 2024 年选举的重要州。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/biden-to-award-8-2-billion-boosting-rail-in-key-2024-states</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 21:51:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>银行高管和立法者在参议院听证会上跳过烟花表演</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2023-12-06/bank-executives-lawmakers-skip-the-fireworks-at-senate-hearing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这是华盛顿版，关于国家首都金钱、权力和政治的时事通讯。今天，白宫记者乔什·温格罗夫 (Josh Wingrove) 报道了银行高管在参议院听证会上的表现。在此注册并通过@bpolitics 关注我们。请在此处向我们的编辑发送电子邮件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2023-12-06/bank-executives-lawmakers-skip-the-fireworks-at-senate-hearing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 21:32:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议员要求对以色列使用美国武器进行更多监督</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/warren-colleagues-press-biden-on-israeli-use-of-us-weapons-in-civilian-deaths</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五名民主党参议员敦促拜登政府对以色列使用美国提供的武器进行更多监督，以确保它们不会造成更多平民伤亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/warren-colleagues-press-biden-on-israeli-use-of-us-weapons-in-civilian-deaths</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 20:41:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将免除近 50 亿美元的学生贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/nearly-5-billion-in-student-debt-forgiveness-announced-by-biden</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登周三决定免除 48 亿美元的学生贷款，为超过 80,000 名借款人提供了救济，其中包括公共部门雇员和几十年来一直在偿还联邦债务的美国人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/nearly-5-billion-in-student-debt-forgiveness-announced-by-biden</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 20:38:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>G-7 将于明年开始禁止俄罗斯钻石</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/g-7-moves-to-ban-russian-diamonds-starting-next-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[七国集团同意从明年初起禁止进口俄罗斯钻石，这是遏制俄罗斯资助其入侵乌克兰的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/g-7-moves-to-ban-russian-diamonds-starting-next-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 20:08:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大将通过限额与交易制度遏制石油和天然气排放</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/canada-to-curb-oil-and-gas-emissions-with-cap-and-trade-regime</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大计划使用总量控制与交易体系来限制该国石油和天然气行业的排放，这项政策将成为总理贾斯汀·特鲁多帮助遏制全球变暖的基石，并且几乎肯定会遇到西部省份的阻力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/canada-to-curb-oil-and-gas-emissions-with-cap-and-trade-regime</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 19:57:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克因争取卢旺达妥协而失去移民部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/uk-s-cleverly-says-immigration-minister-jenrick-has-quit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国移民部长因首相里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)最新提出的将寻求庇护者驱逐到卢旺达的提议而辞职，这凸显了人们对反移民计划不足以平息执政党叛乱的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/uk-s-cleverly-says-immigration-minister-jenrick-has-quit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 19:12:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯铀进口禁令为美国众议院投票做好准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/russian-uranium-import-ban-teed-up-for-us-house-floor-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[禁止俄罗斯浓缩铀进口到美国的立法已准备好在美国众议院进行投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/russian-uranium-import-ban-teed-up-for-us-house-floor-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 19:07:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京罕见会见沙特王储以加强两国关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/putin-meets-uae-ruler-on-rare-trip-to-shore-up-gulf-oil-ties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京在对海湾地区进行的罕见出访中会见了沙特王储穆罕默德·本·萨勒曼，此次访问旨在加强伙伴关系，并抵制美国和欧洲在全球舞台上孤立他的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/putin-meets-uae-ruler-on-rare-trip-to-shore-up-gulf-oil-ties</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 12:50:55 GMT</pubDate>
